  <header class="article-header">
    <h1>Women Speak Out on Why Shaving Their Heads Was One of Their Most Inspired Moments</h1>
    <div class="by-line">
      <a title="Zak Cheney-Rice's Profile" class="link-author avatar avatar-small" href="../../profiles/29788/zak-cheney-rice">
        <img alt="Zak Cheney-Rice's avatar image" class="no-share-btns" src="http://media3.mic.com/ZjEyNzU3ZDE0ZSMvSHhzTTVuOHZ3aUJZeEFTY3pxUUllaVEyWEdvPS8yNXgyNS9zbWFydC9odHRwczovL3MzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20vcG9saWN5bWljLWltYWdlcy84OTk0OTY5M2Y4OWY3MzMyYmI2NTMzYmE1YzdmYjcyNWNkZGRmOTlkOTIzMjcxYjYzNWFjMDVlMTE5MjZmZTE3LmpwZw==.jpg">
      </a>
      By
      <a title="Zak Cheney-Rice's Profile" class="link-author name" href="../../profiles/29788/zak-cheney-rice">Zak Cheney-Rice</a>
      <time datetime="2015-11-06T17:10:07.000Z" pubdate="">November 06, 2015</time>
    </div>
    <div class="share-facebook-twitter subhead">
      <span class="fb-like-container-text">Like Mic on Facebook:</span>
      <span class="fb-button">
        <div class="fb-like-top fb-like" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/MicMedia" data-width="300" data-keen-tracking-name="subhed" data-keen-social-channel="facebook" data-show-faces="false" data-send="false" data-layout="button"></div>
      </span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div id="article-body" class="article-body share-media-toolbar-block"><div class="share-media share-media-side-fold">
  <ul><li class="share-media-facebook"><div class="share-button-count"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128026%2Fwomen-speak-out-on-why-shaving-their-heads-was-one-of-their-most-inspired-moments" title="Share on Facebook" rel:gt_act="share/facebook/share" rel:gt_label="true" name="fb_share" target="_new" class="share-button share-button-medium-facebook modal-trigger-facebook k-trackable-share" data-fb-link="http://mic.com/articles/128026/women-speak-out-on-why-shaving-their-heads-was-one-of-their-most-inspired-moments" data-keen-tracking-name="sidefold-share" data-keen-social-channel="facebook" data-popup-height="380" data-popup-width="660" data-facebook-pixel-id="6028307499936"><i class="social-icon-mini social-icon-mini-facebook"></i><i class="social-icon-divider"></i>SHARE</a></div></li>
